Generic single-database configuration for Telegram Quiz NFT Platform.

## Running Migrations

### Create a new migration
```bash
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "Description of changes"
```

### Apply migrations
```bash
alembic upgrade head
```

### Rollback one migration
```bash
alembic downgrade -1
```

### View current revision
```bash
alembic current
```

### View migration history
```bash
alembic history
```
